column2: Were you already hired or did you have a scholarship before completing the course?
column4: Has your employment situation improved (contract, scholarship or improvement in it)?
column5: Would you consider that the completion of the course has helped in any way to obtain your current contract/scholarship?
column6: Are you using what you learned during the course in your current job?
column7: Have you signed any publication in which you used what you studied during the course?
column8: Nowadays, in perspective, how would you assess the course carried out?
column9: If you have taken other Bioinformatics courses, how would you rate this course compared to them, with 5 just as useful?
